                <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">Multi-provider conversation workspace with streaming SSE support.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card">
                <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🎨</span>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;">Image Generator</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">Text-to-image synthesis models supporting custom dimensions.</p>
