                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Pro Plan</h3>
                    <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;" id="price-pro">$49<span style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:500; color:var(--text-muted);">/mo</span></div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Full access to all 17 AI tools, custom API keys support, and higher speeds.</p>
